name: IC DooM 2003 : 'Yet More DooMing' *Bug Fix*
description: This is a single level, Single Player/Co-Op wad. Turned out to be pretty damn big and probably quite tough, though I have made a bit of an effort to make it easier on 'I don't want to Die' and 'Hurt me Plenty'. Personally I think the level plays better on these settings.
